      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Rubinart's Apparition$<BR>So you think it's a lie? Oh, Rita, the flowers are just right here. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(The red dragon pulls a snow-white flower off of the shelf.)</FONT><BR>Now, can you show me the materials you got?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2947_rubinat-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Rubinart's Apparition$<BR>What? This isn't the jewel of the sea I told you about. Are you sure you brought the right one?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2947_rubinat-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2947_rubinat-3-d" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#7e12d2>(The materials become entangled, and it gradually begins to take shape.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Rubinart's Apparition$<BR>Oh, you really came, did you? Then let's see, first this, then do this, that, and over here...<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Rubinart begins to weave the ingredients together.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2947_rubinat-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2947_rubinat-3-e" mid="40" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>That’s it? It’s just an accessory...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Rubinart's Apparition$<BR>There, finished. With this, your safety will be ensured by its blessing.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(The red dragon hands over the Amulet it has just made.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2947_rubinat-3-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2947_rubinat-3-f" mid="42" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Is there anything else?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$Rubinart's Apparition$<BR>Yes, yes – try it on. We haven’t finished yet.<BR>Oh, I forgot to mention this before.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2947_rubinat-3-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2947_rubinat-3-g" mid="44" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes? What?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Rubinart's Apparition$<BR>Accept this, and my blessing will protect you. But at the same time, because of my strength, you can summon my jewel from anywhere, and it will find you.<BR>That is the reason I am here – for the power to summon my jewel. It receives the effect here.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2947_rubinat-3-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2947_rubinat-3-h" mid="46" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#2b2723>My... there were so many questions I had wanted to ask you. (He puts on the Amulet.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Rubinart's Apparition$<BR>But this is the power that will protect you. Please don’t despise it.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2947_rubinat-3-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2947_rubinat-3-i" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Is this it?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Rubinart's Apparition$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(As the red dragon's conceptual apparition touches the amulet, bit by bit, a warm energy seems to gather.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2947_rubinat-3-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2947_rubinat-3-j" mid="50" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>$Rubinart's Apparition$<BR>That's right. Whenever the time comes, my power sealed in this amulet will be able to protect you.<BR>But equally as much, it will make finding you easier...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2947_rubinat-3-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2947_rubinat-3-k" mid="52" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I'm the one who tries harder than anybody to stay alive.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$Rubinart's Apparition$<BR>The blessing protects you, but I don't know about this body.<BR>Be careful not to swallow it; I want you to be safe from mishaps.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2947_rubinat-3-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2947_rubinat-3-l" mid="54" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#7e12d2>(The Red Dragon has disappeared.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
